com.github.mangstadt.vinnie

Class VObjectParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.mangstadt.vinnie.VObjectParameters
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<Map.Entry<String,List<String>>>

    public class VObjectParameters
extends Object
implements Iterable<Map.Entry<String,List<String>>>
    A simple multimap implementation for holding the parameters of a VObjectProperty. Enforces case-insensitivity of parameter names by converting them to uppercase.
    Author:
    Michael Angstadt

    • Constructor Detail

      • VObjectParameters

        public VObjectParameters()
        Creates an empty list of parameters.

      • VObjectParameters

        public VObjectParameters(Map<String,List<String>> map)

        Creates a list of parameters backed by the given map. Any changes made to the given map will effect the parameter list and vice versa.

        If the given map is not empty, care should be taken to ensure that all of its keys are in uppercase before passing it into this constructor.

        Parameters:
        map - the map

      • VObjectParameters
